parameters: \n<Polteghost>You defeated my slaves! Now, I will destroy you!
\n<Bandits Leader> Fantastic! You managed to defeat my ninjas!
Now, try me and my Elite!
\n<Bandits Leader> You Win! But, our Lord Polterghost will avenge us!
\n<Zarie>We fought the Polterghost for the book? What's with those books anyway?
\n<Dwayne>We need the Seven Books of Eli to get the Mirror of Eli.
\n<Zarie>And what is that mirror all about?
\n<Dwayne>Once we have that mirror, we can ask anything we want and
it'll give us the exact answer, including where we can find the missing
people, including Philip's sister and my mother.
\n<Zarie>Well, sounds like, killing more gargoyles! I like it!
\n<Zarie>Let's just get going and ask around.
\n<Dwayne>I think that's that best thing we should do.
